- @title = "Class Schedule"

section.schedule-overview
  .paintbrush-light.top
  .container
    h2 Schedule
    p We don't rely heavily on <em>advanced</em> and <em>beginner</em> as there are so many other factors that might play in — age, fitness level, ability to learn new material, or even the ability of a student to attend one day and not another. If you don't know which class is a good fit, we recommend you talk to Sifu about it.

    hr
    h3 Notes on Class Cancellation
    p There are times when due to circumstances beyond our control, class is cancelled with somewhat short notice. When this happens, we'll send out emails to everyone on our list. If you're not getting our emails already, feel free to sign up using the form at the bottom of this page.


