    h2 Flexible Options
    p Our class schedule is designed to accommodate as many people as we can. We realize that most of the students and families at Great Way have busy lives and other activities — we're always willing to chat with you to try and find the best option.
    p If the current schedule does not fit your needs, you'd like to focus on something else, or you're just not sure where you fit best, please feel free to email your Sifu or Todai to set up a time to chat.



